		<div id="comment_body_64642206"><p>All countries should be doing more to boost their economies.</p><p>There are loads of jobs making wind turbines and solar panels, and then even more jobs installing and maintaining them.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64642206">

